sentence: Hi @amadio, I think I found the problem. We simply need to add dependencies on libVecOps.so. For the dependency of PyROOT on VecOps, we can discuss a solution together with @etejedor. I have an idea on how to solve this relying on the fact that a TVec has the same layout of a vector with a custom allocator.
